title: Boston Dynamics Impressive New Robot Can Jump Over Obstacles, Which Means There's Nowhere Left To Hide
text: Blacklist domain ONE GIANT LEAP FOR ROBOTKIND Boston Dynamics Impressive New Robot Can Jump Over Obstacles, Which Means There's Nowhere Left To Hide 0 diggs Technology Design Video The robot, called Handle, can also pick up heavy loads in its "hands," roll down stairs, jump on tables, and generally do a bunch of stuff that will make it easier to track us down and eliminate us one by one.
